Exception: Exception is an un-expected event that occurs during the execution of program which disrupts the normal flow of execution
           and leads to abnormal termination.

ArrayIndexOfBoundsException
ArithmeticException
StringIndexOutOfBoundsException
 
Exception Handling :
           Exception Handling is a mechanism for handling run-time errors to ensure application regular flow is maintained.
             
             
             
